{"pageProps":{"currentData":{"ID":243333,"author":"1","author_nickname":"wpuser","author_display_name":"Chuckie Chang","author_url":"https://matrixflip.com/api","author_username":"wpuser","author_avatar":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=96&d=mm&r=g","categories":[25],"categories_output":[{"ID":25,"slug":"%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb%e7%90%90%e7%a2%8e","name":"生活琐碎","term_taxonomy_id":25,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":0,"count":30}],"tags":[35,266,260,27,268,267],"tags_output":[{"ID":35,"slug":"%e5%85%8d%e8%b4%b9%e5%bb%ba%e7%ab%99","name":"免费建站","term_taxonomy_id":35,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":2},{"ID":266,"slug":"%e5%a4%8f%e5%ad%a3","name":"夏季","term_taxonomy_id":266,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1},{"ID":260,"slug":"%e6%b8%b8%e6%88%8f","name":"游戏","term_taxonomy_id":260,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":2},{"ID":27,"slug":"%e8%a1%97%e8%88%9e","name":"街舞","term_taxonomy_id":27,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":4},{"ID":268,"slug":"%e8%b7%91%e9%85%b7","name":"跑酷","term_taxonomy_id":268,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1},{"ID":267,"slug":"%e9%85%b7%e6%9a%91","name":"酷暑","term_taxonomy_id":267,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1}],"thumbnail":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_2ffd95ec5e42497c109d39e2-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomffdececdexjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_2ffd95ec5e42497c109d39e2-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomffdececdexxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_2ffd95ec5e42497c109d39e2-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomffdececdexjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_full":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_2ffd95ec5e42497c109d39e2-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomffdececdexjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"date_day":"31","date_month":"08","date_month_e":"August","date_year":"2013","date_weekday":"Saturday","title":"夏天一过，终于恢复点精神","excerpt":"夏天一过，终于恢复点精神，那一久经常跑去超市吹空调降温。真的很不爽。工作效率极低的天气。好好打起精神啦。","content":"<p><span>夏天一过，终于恢复点精神，那一久经常跑去超市吹空调降温。真的很不爽。工作效率极低的天气。</span></p>\n<p>记得那7、8月份练舞的时候，那汗啊，和水差不多。</p>\n<p>去沙地上练跑酷的的踢月转体和踢月翻的那段时间，一旦自己摔倒沙里，啊哈，你可以想象，满身的沙，眼睛、鼻子、甚至内裤里。不过嘛，为了喜欢的动作去努力锻炼，心酸又满足。</p>\n<p>唯一的好基友短裤大人经常在我家睡，哎哟，搅基也是一种浪漫。谁让单身的我那么孤单呢。</p>\n<p>看看我们一大家一起Happy跳舞的日子吧，呵呵</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/images/98889de2ff1c45742cd16d68-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsdeffccddjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> <img src=\"/static-remote/images/401e341be4705b5481c95a74-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsebebcajpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> <img src=\"/static-remote/images/3c0d1da1ab4d5fb26cc2effc-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadscddaabdfbcceffcjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>夏天一过，代表即将开始新的生活，基友也上学了，我也有很多事情要做了。还得常去dribbble里发作品。艾莫，这只有拼的生活，啥时才是个尽头呢。</p>\n<p>再过不久就到游戏公司工作了，开始新的旅途咯。当然网页我是不会放弃的，毕竟有自己的产品要运营和更新嘛 ：-）</p>\n<p>一直在努力，从未退缩过！</p>\n","slug":"7d7ce6b80ad70ea3e1c1e783","prev":[{"ID":63333,"title":"致我最后的青春","excerpt":"这一切，其实也是一种惩罚：一旦你拥有自己喜欢的东西之后，可能你就再也无法接受其它不喜欢的东西,其实，这不是我最后的青春，还有很长很长的路要走，这只是我最后得到的青春。","slug":"35ec468d38b6f86c230d36b6","post_date":"2013-05-11 13:54:47","post_date_gmt":"2013-05-11 13:54:47","thumbnail":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_63fe42345ce83a1f186450f7-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfeceaffxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_63fe42345ce83a1f186450f7-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfeceaffxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_63fe42345ce83a1f186450f7-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfeceaffxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"next":[{"ID":253333,"title":"2014,又是多少割舍不下的情怀","excerpt":"一路走来，除了离别还是离别。就直接算到2014年吧，又有多少割舍不下的情怀。呆了几年的城市，也得因为工作原因转移，毕竟要挣更多的钱，要不断更新升级，才能适应时代需求，去享受，去养活自己，去实现梦想。除了原...","slug":"2014-life-no-less-than-give-feelings","post_date":"2013-09-12 01:02:29","post_date_gmt":"2013-09-12 01:02:29","thumbnail":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_c8d9cda66b0eeed0af442fe8-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomcdcdabeeedaffexjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_c8d9cda66b0eeed0af442fe8-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomcdcdabeeedaffexxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_c8d9cda66b0eeed0af442fe8-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomcdcdabeeedaffexjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"post_date":"2013-08-31 09:31:05","post_date_gmt":"2013-08-31 09:31:05","post_status":"publish","comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","post_password":"","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2013-08-31 09:31:05","post_modified_gmt":"2013-08-31 09:31:05","post_content_filtered":"","post_parent":0,"guid":"https://matrixflip.com/api/?post_type=post&amp;p=243333","menu_order":0,"post_type":"post","post_mime_type":"","comment_count":"0","filter":"raw"}},"__N_SSG":true}